Package in.co.rays.proj4.controller

Interface ORSView

  • public interface ORSView
    Author:
    Aniket Rajput ORSView interface contains constants for all the views and controllers in the ORS (Online Result System) Project.

    It provides a centralized place to define:

    • Application context
    • Folder paths for JSP pages
    • Mapping of views (JSP) to their respective controllers (CTL)

    Use Case:

    • Helps avoid spelling mistakes in URLs and file paths
    • Makes it easy to update paths in one place without searching the entire code

    This interface is implemented by servlets or used by controllers to get the path of the required JSP page or controller.
